nt in North Lawndale and/or Englewood. What is important is that they are in the community preparing a research topic to discuss as well as interviewing and surveying the community to learn more about the health disparities that are prevalent. They will then collect that information and present to the Health at WORC team at the end of the quarter. ','2','Sunday, Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, Friday and/or Saturday','','','','','','','','','','','','','No','False',null,'False',null,'False',null,'Winter Quarter,Spring Quarter','','25','Yes','Yes','Cristy Miles','Director of Health at WORC','10/2/12 12:00:00 AM','');
